{"tid":1447350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我一個月前已經預言，前線班勇武就係鬼 + 分享反送中運動嘅未來必勝策略","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:49:34.000Z","uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c84ca90e164a1623d93057f05279007c9e9ab18","tid":1447350,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"我一早已經同大家講過，前細有一班勇武派係鬼，不過呢度有大量mon post犬俾負皮，沉咗底。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候邊個仲叫勇武即係送後生仔去坐監<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n<br />\n早幾日，我同大家講過，只參加維園合法集會，集會後即散，但同樣又俾mon post犬俾負皮。沉咗底，如果大家認真睇，今日會係0被捕。<br />\n<br />\n811只參加維園集會後即散，大家點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435776</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於未來策略如何？一陣再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9fab66592ec15a1982f4a28d11d5fa6ac8ac7e","tid":1447350,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32b252a0faa7e5631bfe31685188979be992159","tid":1447350,"uid":57594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 P牌"},{"pid":"90e5f7ba312eb9eadbccef52253612293ff513c8","tid":1447350,"uid":274513,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d32b252a0faa7e5631bfe31685188979be992159","tid":1447350,"uid":57594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 P牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"警犬一隻發現<br />\n<br />\n好驚我地覺醒，你地煽唔到我地，捉唔到人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1938c00d8560d3ef7b485b8cf756eb0732187d","tid":1447350,"uid":124292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:53: